#: restrict-usernames-emails-characters.php:773
#, php-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Your database contains a user (%1$s) with invalid letters or characters. "
#| "It is recommended that you enable the &#34;Solved the problem of not "
#| "being able to register with certain languages&#34; option if you "
#| "previously allowed these characters and then disallowed them, and you "
#| "still have users with these characters in the database. Otherwise, if you "
#| "never allowed these characters, simply delete these names without "
#| "enabling this option."
msgid ""
"Your database contains a user(s): (%1$s) with invalid letters or characters. "
"It is recommended that you enable the &#34;Solved the problem of not being "
"able to register with certain languages&#34; option if you previously "
"allowed these characters and then disallowed them, and you still have users "
"with these characters in the database. Otherwise, if you never allowed these "
"characters, simply delete these names without enabling this option."
msgstr ""
"يوجد في قاعدة بياناتك اسم أو أسماء مستخدمين (%1$s) تحتوي على أحرف أو رموز "
"غير صالحة, أي ممنوعة. يُنصح بتفعيل خيار &#34;حل مشكل عدم القدرة على التسجيل "
"مع بعض اللغات&#34; إذا كنت قد سمحت بهذه الأحرف سابقًا ثم حظرتها، ولا يزال "
"لديك أسماء في قاعدة البيانات تحتوي على هذه الحروف الممنوعة حاليا. أما إذا لم "
"تسمح بهذه الأحرف مطلقًا من قبل، فما عليك سوى حذف هذه الأسماء دون تفعيل هذا "
"الخيار."

